ModelView Controller Framework:
	  ->Controller
	  |	/		\
	View<-------Model

	Model:
		manages the behavior and data of app
		When modelupdated view also update the represenation

	View:
		Renders the Model

	Controller:
		Recive info from the User,then instruct the Model,simultaneously instruct the view.

Angular Modules:
	-MVC
	-MVVC
	-MVW

	Angular Module is a Collection of:
		Controllers
		Directives
		Filters
		Service

		<html ngApp="confusionApp">

		<body>

			<script>
				var app = angular.module('confusionApp',[]);
			</script>
		</body>
		</html>

	Angular Controller:
		A javascript Object
			<div class="" ng-controller="menuController">

			</div>
			<script>
				var app=angular.module("appname",[]);
				app.menuController('menuController'){

				});
			</script>

